00:38:42,500 --> 00:38:44,740
You're seeing the unified theory of the paper now.

745
00:38:44,840 --> 00:38:45,580
It all connects.

746
00:38:45,580 --> 00:38:55,220
By forcing a sequential global clock over a computing system, we artificially inflate the thermodynamic cost of intelligence.

747
00:38:55,360 --> 00:38:56,740
We're basically wasting energy.

748
00:38:56,920 --> 00:39:04,540
We force unnecessary synchronization, endless idle waiting, and repeated serialization of data that hasn't even changed.

749
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:09,580
MEM8 achieves stability not through brute force rigidity, but through resonance.

750
00:39:09,580 --> 00:39:15,300
It keeps the cognitive architecture alive while doing the absolute minimum amount of thermodynamic work.

751
00:39:15,520 --> 00:39:19,400
Okay, all of this talk about coherence and stabilization and harmonic lock.

